description:
If you're looking for worship songs that are sure to get you close to God, then look no further than Near the Cross! This song is sure to touch your heart and fill you with the Holy Spirit. In this karaoke video, you'll get to experience their amazing music firsthand. enjoy!

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters karaoke youtube channel.
First Line: Jesus, keep me near the cross
Title: Near the Cross
Author: Fanny Crosby (1869)
